WEBVTT

1
00:00:20.166 --> 00:00:21.966
Since the emperor's illness has been cured

2
00:00:21.966 --> 00:00:23.666
Then I'll go back to the cold palace

3
00:00:26.466 --> 00:00:28.700
Don't go back and take care of people for so long

4
00:00:28.766 --> 00:00:30.233
This is a surprise for you.

5
00:00:31.566 --> 00:00:34.600
How about Miss Jiang, do you like this surprise?

6
00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:37.066
Hmm, Chu Mo, um

7
00:00:37.566 --> 00:00:39.300
I want this. Okay.

8
00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:44.166
Chu Mo, this is for you.

9
00:00:45.533 --> 00:00:47.900
I know you have a thorn in your heart

10
00:00:47.900 --> 00:00:49.200
It's a portrait.

11
00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:52.066
He is far less in my heart than you

12
00:00:52.066 --> 00:00:54.100
He is my savior and subordinate

13
00:00:54.333 --> 00:00:55.833
But you are my only one

14
00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:58.433
The emperor can have many people in his heart

15
00:00:58.466 --> 00:01:01.666
But in the concubine's heart, there is only the emperor

16
00:01:01.666 --> 00:01:04.500
Don't worry, I will dismiss the harem when I go back.

17
00:01:04.600 --> 00:01:06.166
Since you are my only one

18
00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:08.400
I want to be your only one too

